FIRST PAID PRODUCTS — detailed:

  1. Basic Listing Check — ₹499
     Contents: Price sanity check, area sanity, locality comparison,
               RERA match or no-match flag
     Target: First-time homebuyers, anyone evaluating a 99acres listing

  2. Project Risk Report — ₹1,499
     Contents: Builder track record, RERA status, complaint history,
               timeline delays, anomaly flags, data inconsistencies
     Target: Buyers evaluating a specific under-construction project

  3. Investor Locality Pack — ₹4,999
     Contents: Price trends for locality, filtered listings (bad ones removed),
               risky project list, opportunity zones with growth signals
     Target: Land investors, NRIs, small real estate funds

  4. Monthly City Dashboard — ₹9,999/month
     Contents: All active Akola/Amravati listings + RERA project risk status
               + price trends, updated every month
     Target: Local brokers, consultants, institutional investors

